statistics <- list(
      ` ` = ~length(.x),
      ` ( )` = ~sum(!is.na(.x)),
      ` ` = ~sum(is.na(.x)),
      `. .` = ~ifelse(sum(!is.na(.x)) == 0, "/*", mean(.x, na.rm = TRUE) %>% round(2) %>% as.character()),
      `. .` = ~ifelse(sum(!is.na(.x)) < 3, "/*", sd(.x, na.rm = TRUE) %>% round(2) %>% as.character()),
      `. - .` = ~ifelse(sum(!is.na(.x)) == 0, "/*", paste0(min(.x, na.rm = TRUE) %>% round(2), " - ", max(.x, na.rm = TRUE) %>% round(2))),
      `` = ~ifelse(sum(!is.na(.x)) == 0, "/*", median(.x, na.rm = TRUE) %>% round(2) %>% as.character()),
      `Q1 - Q3` = ~ifelse(sum(!is.na(.x)) == 0, "/*", paste0(quantile(.x, 0.25, na.rm = TRUE) %>% round(2), " - ", quantile(.x, 0.75, na.rm = TRUE) %>% round(2)))
)
df1_na_all <- df1_na %>%
  mutate(`/` = "")
df1_na_work <- rbind(df1_na, df1_na_all)
stat_num_res <- df1_na_work %>%
  select(`/`, where(is.numeric)) %>%
  group_by(`/`) %>%
  summarise(across(where(is.numeric), statistics)) %>%
  mutate(across(everything(), as.character)) %>% 
  pivot_longer(!`/`) %>%
  separate(name, into  = c("",""), sep = "_") %>% 
  dcast(`` + `` ~ `/`, value.var = "value") 
stat_num_res %>% 
  flextable() %>%
  theme_box() %>%
  merge_v(c( "")) %>%
  set_caption("   ")
